{"TopicId":223569,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Weather?","CreatedByName":"blanoun","CreatedById":232586,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-08T00:58:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"blanoun","CreatedById":232586,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-08T00:58:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if KSP2 had specific weather for each planet.\u00A0 For example, Duna\u0027s IRL counterpart is known to experience planet-wide dust storms, so what if there was something like that in KSP2.\u00A0 Then the other atmospheric planets such as Laythe and Eve could have massive thunderstorms.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cinnamondamoth","CreatedById":232867,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-03T21:33:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how to feel about this, on one hand it\u0027d be a cool addition, but on the other hand it\u0027d make missions more difficult and would require some sort of weather forecast system (more probe centric parts?) to not just annoy you to death. The game already lacks tools to precisely land (no waypoints \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E) and so an MVP of this feature would probably be \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ereally\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E annoying to deal with.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nTLDR: I don\u0027t think it should be added right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Presto200","CreatedById":232857,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-04T16:33:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224370050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221709501626\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232867\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cinnamondamoth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, cinnamondamoth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how to feel about this, on one hand it\u0027d be a cool addition, but on the other hand it\u0027d make missions more difficult and would require some sort of weather forecast system (more probe centric parts?) to not just annoy you to death.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree it would\u00A0 not be good for base gameplay (especially for new players) but it could be cool if it was just for looks and then if you selected \u0022Hard\u0022 mode then it could actually effect flight. Or if it was a toggle setting in the menus.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also think that the devs have a lot more important things to prioritize so I don\u0027t think this should be implemented now either\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cinnamondamoth","CreatedById":232867,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-04T18:30:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224370184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221709569985\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232857\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Presto200\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Presto200 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree it would\u00A0 not be good for base gameplay (especially for new players) but it could be cool if it was just for looks and then if you selected \u0022Hard\u0022 mode then it could actually effect flight. Or if it was a toggle setting in the menus.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also think that the devs have a lot more important things to prioritize so I don\u0027t think this should be implemented now either\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes but it\u0027d require a way to predict the weather, something akin to a weather satellite maybe? Since it\u0027d suck to land in awful weather due to random chance and not have any way to predict it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CoolSpace","CreatedById":227003,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-06T19:05:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think Weather would work well if it was used only in science; players could travel around and collect science using some sort of weather analyzer part, and instead of going to different biomes you would go to different areas with different weather at that time; Sunny, cloudy, rainy, storms, northern lights etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also think places like Joel should get some lighting effects so it is much more dramatic decending into it\u0027s lower atmosphere (This would of course require a new soundtrack for storms \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-03-06T19:06:11Z\u0022 title=\u002203/06/2024 07:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Mar 6\u0022\u003EMarch 6\u003C/time\u003E by CoolSpace\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CameronLeroux","CreatedById":232166,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-11T13:30:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the idea but it would have to interfere with communication between vessels and probes to make it realistic and it would also have solar panels being unusable for a certain amount of time. Same thing with launching rockets where it would add more challenge to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaypeg","CreatedById":228190,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-20T01:03:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts something that is considered for near 1.0, sadly, but its being thought about\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flush Foot","CreatedById":193460,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-20T03:09:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224373943\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710896614\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228190\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jaypeg\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Jaypeg said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts something that is considered for near 1.0, sadly, but its being thought about\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd how do you know this? Was weather in a Dev Diary / Interview somewhere?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaypeg","CreatedById":228190,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-20T22:56:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224373968\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710904191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flush Foot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, Flush Foot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd how do you know this? Was weather in a Dev Diary / Interview somewhere?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the discord, when asked about auroras for planets\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-20T22:58:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224373968\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710904191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022193460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flush Foot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, Flush Foot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd how do you know this? Was weather in a Dev Diary / Interview somewhere?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224374163\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710975409\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228190\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jaypeg\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Jaypeg said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the discord,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course it was.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flush Foot","CreatedById":193460,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-21T00:29:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224374165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710975538\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course it was.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTell me about it \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaypeg","CreatedById":228190,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-21T01:24:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224374165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710975538\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course it was.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe discord just has a channel that is a compilation of all dev comments/leeks. They said they are planning some atmospheric changes (because they have blackrack now) and auroras for poles is planned.\u003Cbr\u003E\nLots of cool stuff can be done with weather, lets compile some ideas!\u003Cbr\u003E\nMy ideas: a planet with superstorms that destroy crafts. To go to it you have to land, get sceince then leave before one of the massive storms on the horizon gets to you. That would be sick.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso steam venting on eve, that lift up crafts when they fly into them\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd dust storms on Duna\u003Cbr\u003E\nRain on kerbin\u003Cbr\u003E\nLarge storms on laythe (rainy)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nLightning, in general, would be sick\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd ofc weather-based science. And turbulence\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flush Foot","CreatedById":193460,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-21T01:40:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224374196\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221710984276\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228190\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jaypeg\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, Jaypeg said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe discord just has a channel that is a compilation of all dev comments/leeks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes\u2026 \u201CDev tracker\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JLesM18.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022200.60\u0022 height=\u00221200\u0022 width=\u0022973\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JLesM18.jpeg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u2019t see atmospheric anything\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaypeg","CreatedById":228190,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-21T02:26:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ip